[{"id":"fd0b28e71af1063573e84dfac78ceda9","from":"Rich Kahn","from_email":"rkahn@nysgmail.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: Bank Wire Instructions","date":"2007-11-29T18:05:45.000Z","formatted_date":"Nov 29, 2007","formatted_time":"6:05 PM","body":"As per your request I will send this wire today.  Should I have Cerulean\nprepare a package which we can messenger to Doctor Kruger as we did last\nyear?\n\n \n\nFYI - regarding Dan Nardello as of 12:45pm today the 10,000 has not yet\nbeen received.\n\n \n\nRich Kahn\n\nNew York Strategy Group LLC\n\n457 Madison Avenue\n\nFourth Floor\n\nNew York, NY 10022\n\ntel  212-891-6430\n\nfax 212-750-2408\n\nrkahn@nysgmail.com\n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Dawn Dine [mailto:ddine@ceruleanjet.com] \nSent: Thursday, November 29, 2007 12:51 PM\nTo: Rich Kahn\nSubject: Bank Wire Instructions\n\n \n\n \n<http://na2.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?oid=00D3000000013\nNJ&id=01540000000BEtK> \n\n \n\nDear Rich,\n\n \n\nThank you for selecting Cerulean Jet.  Mr. Kruger currently has a\n$7138.62 credit on his account.  I am happy to extend the exact same\ncontract and terms as signed on December 1st, 2006.  With the $25,000.00\ngift card for Mr. Kruger, he will have a credit of  $32,138.62 toward\nhis future flights.  By wiring the funds for Mr. Kruger, that will\nconstitute as signature and acceptance of the terms and conditions of\nhis current contract.\n\n \n\nHere are our wire transfer instructions:\n\n \n\n            Wachovia Bank, Woodstock, GA\n\n            ABA number: 061000227\n\n            For credit to: Cerulean Jet, Inc.\n\n            Account number: 2000035533906            \n\n            Reference your last name and/or company name\n\n             \n\n\n\nTotal amount to be wired: $__25,000.00___.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nWe truly appreciate your business and look forward to servicing your jet\ncharter needs for years to come.\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nKindest Regards,\n\n\n\n\nDawn Dine\nVice President\n(877) 692-5385 ext. 704\nddine@ceruleanjet.com\n\n \n\n \n<http://na2.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?oid=00D3000000013\nNJ&id=01540000000BF3K> \n\n \n\n \n<http://na2.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?oid=00D3000000013\nNJ&esid=01840000006WPx1> \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:st1=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 11 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]--><o:SmartTagType\n namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" name=\"PostalCode\"/>\n<o:SmartTagType namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"\n name=\"State\"/>\n<o:SmartTagType namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"\n name=\"City\"/>\n<o:SmartTagType namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"\n name=\"place\"/>\n<o:SmartTagType namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"\n name=\"Street\"/>\n<o:SmartTagType namespaceuri=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\"\n name=\"address\"/>\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nst1\\:*{behavior:url(#default#ieooui) }\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Tahoma;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 4 3 5 4 4 2 4;}\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0in;\n\tmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{color:blue;\n\ttext-decoration:und